Package: PortfolioAttribution
Type: Package
Title: Performance attribution tools used for identifying sources of portfolio return and risk.
Version: 1.0
Date: $Date$
Author: Andrii Babii
Maintainer: Anand Krishnakumar <andykris21@yahoo.com>
Description: This package provides functions for the ex-post portfolio attribution methods described in Christopherson, Carino and Ferson (2009), Bacon (2008), and several other sources. The package was initially created as a part of the Google Summer of Code (GSoC) 2012 project. Since then it has undergone some minor enhancements & revisions for accuracy, consistency and improved usability.
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    testthat
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.0),
    PerformanceAnalytics(>= 1.0.4.3),
    xts (>= 0.8),
    zoo
Suggests:
    FinancialInstrument,
    knitr,
    plyr,
    rmarkdown
